        "origin": "web-extension",
        "content": "<p> Taken from Shakespeare (d. 1025/1616) <em>The Life of Henry V</em>: “… a good heart, Kate, is the sun and the moon—or rather the sun and not the moon, for it shines bright and never changes, but keeps his course truly.”  </p>",
        "sectionId": "web-extension-speaking-the-truth-with-love"
