        "content": "<p> (Ecclesiastes, 1:11). The passage is about the loss of meaning. It is attributed to the Prophet Soloman and begins: “Meaningless! Meaningless!” says the Teacher. “Utterly meaningless! Everything is meaningless” (Ecclesiastes, 1:2). </p>",
